---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Case Study: GolfSimMap" description="How GolfSimMap launched and entered post-launch growth phase.">
  <section class="pt-24 pb-14">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <span class="text-sm text-[#8b5cf6] font-['JetBrains_Mono'] tracking-wider">CASE STUDY</span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mt-4 mb-4 font-['Space_Grotesk']">GolfSimMap.com</h1>
      <p class="text-[#8b8b9a] text-lg max-w-3xl">A modern golf simulator directory built for speed, discoverability, and commercial intent. Launched in Feb 2026 and now in post-launch growth mode.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="pb-8">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="aspect-video rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-[#2a2a3a]">
        <img src="/images/portfolio/golfsimmap-hero.png" alt="GolfSimMap hero section" class="w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-10">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
      <div class="bg-[#151520] border border-[#2a2a3a] rounded-xl p-5">
        <p class="text-xs text-[#8b8b9a]">Status</p>
        <p class="text-2xl text-white font-['JetBrains_Mono'] mt-1">Live</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-[#151520] border border-[#2a2a3a] rounded-xl p-5">
        <p class="text-xs text-[#8b8b9a]">Stage</p>
        <p class="text-2xl text-[#8b5cf6] font-['JetBrains_Mono'] mt-1">Early Growth</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-[#151520] border border-[#2a2a3a] rounded-xl p-5">
        <p class="text-xs text-[#8b8b9a]">Positioning</p>
        <p class="text-white mt-1">“The place golfers go before they book a bay.”</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-8">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <div class="bg-[#151520] border border-[#2a2a3a] rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl text-white font-['Space_Grotesk'] mb-4">What was built</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-[#c7c7d2]">
          <li>• Next.js + Supabase architecture for scale</li>
          <li>• Static category configuration for fast pages</li>
          <li>• Canonicals, OG, schema, breadcrumbs, FAQ structure</li>
          <li>• Core templates for city/category discovery</li>
          <li>• Launch-ready UX focused on local search intent</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-[#151520] border border-[#2a2a3a] rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl text-white font-['Space_Grotesk'] mb-4">Current growth priorities</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-[#c7c7d2]">
          <li>• Backlink acquisition every week</li>
          <li>• Indexing coverage growth in GSC</li>
          <li>• Internal linking improvements to money pages</li>
          <li>• City + category content depth expansion</li>
          <li>• Weekly KPI dashboard (impressions/clicks/ref domains)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-8">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="bg-[#0f1119] border border-[#2a2a3a] rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8">
        <h3 class="text-xl text-white font-['Space_Grotesk'] mb-3">Note on traffic</h3>
        <p class="text-[#8b8b9a]">This project launched recently, so long-window traffic benchmarks are still maturing. The public version of this case study will be updated as more performance data accumulates.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
      <a href="https://golfsimmap.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-[#0a0a0f] bg-gradient-to-r from-[#8b5cf6] to-[#a78bfa] rounded-xl hover:shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(139,92,246,0.4)] transition-all">Visit Live Site</a>
      <a href="/portfolio" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white border border-[#2a2a3a] rounded-xl hover:border-[#8b5cf6] hover:shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(139,92,246,0.1)] transition-all glow-border">Back to Portfolio</a>
      <a href="/pricing" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white border border-[#2a2a3a] rounded-xl hover:border-[#00f0ff] hover:shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(0,240,255,0.1)] transition-all glow-border">Start your project</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
